            <title>PS5 手掣劈開兩半自製「PS Portal」【有片睇】中國網紅：價錢便宜一半</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/04/psp/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=psp</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/04/psp/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Christy]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 12:56:15 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[PS Portal]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SONY]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手掣]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1208505</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Sony 最近推出全新 PS Portal 裝置，在這部設計有點像 PS5 手掣劈開兩半再加個熒幕的主機上，遠端遊玩家中的 PS5。由於 PS Portal 手掣僅支援串流 PS5 遊戲，卻索價 199 美元（約 HK1,555）令不少人卻步。然而有中國科技 KOL 在 ChatGPT 的協助下，以半價製作出一部功能與 PS Portal 相近的遊戲裝置。</p><p>中國影片製作者「貪玩歌姬小寧子」近日於 Bilibili 平台上載一條名為「SONY 賣 199 美元的 PSP，自己做，居然只花了 $$$」的影片。小寧子表示自己沒有電子工程基礎，在 ChatGPT 的協助及多次的嘗試和錯誤下，最終以 3 個月自家製出 PS Portal 手掣。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-09.38.25.png"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208563" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-09.38.25-694x346.png" alt="" width="694" height="346" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-09.38.25-694x346.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-09.38.25-1280x639.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-09.38.25-768x383.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-09.38.25-1536x766.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-09.38.25.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>小寧子首先將 DualSense 及電路板用電鋸切成兩半，並重新設計一個分開的 PCB 電路板。在手掣部分，小寧子將網上買的 DualSense 手掣外殼，再從邊緣慢慢切割，把不必要的給拆解掉，便能製作出兩邊分開的搖桿。手掣晶片方面，小寧子選用支援藍牙的 ESP32 晶片，使其自製的手把甚至比 Sony 的多出藍牙功能。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208604" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-19.04.47-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-19.04.47-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-19.04.47-1280x716.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-19.04.47-768x430.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-19.04.47-1536x859.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-19.04.47-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-09.41.23.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208567" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-09.41.23-694x343.png" alt="" width="694" height="343" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-09.41.23-694x343.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-09.41.23-1280x633.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-09.41.23-768x380.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-09.41.23-1536x760.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-09.41.23.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-09.40.47.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208566" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-09.40.47-694x343.png" alt="" width="694" height="343" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-09.40.47-694x343.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-09.40.47-1280x633.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-09.40.47-768x380.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-09.40.47-1536x760.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-09.40.47.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-09.40.00.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208565" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-09.40.00-694x343.png" alt="" width="694" height="343" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-09.40.00-694x343.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-09.40.00-1280x633.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-09.40.00-768x380.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-09.40.00-1536x760.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-09.40.00.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-09.42.00.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208568" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-09.42.00-694x343.png" alt="" width="694" height="343" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-09.42.00-694x343.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-09.42.00-1280x633.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-09.42.00-768x380.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-09.42.00-1536x760.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-09.42.00.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>在研究電路板時，小寧子稱所有問題皆交由 ChatGPT 解決，而大部分的程式也是由 ChatGPT 編寫。小寧子只需向 ChatGPT 詳細描述問題及要求，並檢查其回應，一旦有錯便叫 ChatGPT 更改，因此要知道每個程式碼的作用。最終將畫好的電路圖交由任職工程師的母親審閲其可行性。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/1701493498-4ce8fa5ad670d20fc565736f6534a8f0.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208545" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/1701493498-4ce8fa5ad670d20fc565736f6534a8f0-694x356.png" alt="" width="694" height="356" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023