            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1208438</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>遊戲開發商 Rockstar Games 於上週宣佈，將於週二（5 日）香港時間晚上 10 時發布《GTA 6》首條預告片。離上一代《GTA 5》推出至今已超過 10 年，《GTA 6》預告片推出在即，一眾玩家對此充滿期待。然而近日 TikTok 流傳兩段《GTA 6》的第一視角影片，據悉由 Rockstar Games 開發者的兒子洩露。</p><p>TikTok 用户 i_see_in_4k 於週日（3 日）分別上載兩條 7 秒及 13 秒的影片，並堅稱其為《GTA 6》的第一視角影片。雖然網絡上亦流傳著不少《GTA 6》的洩密片段，但外媒 Eurogamer 認為是次的影片十分可信。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-06.49.58.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1208444" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-06.49.58.png" alt="" width="680" height="550" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-06.50.02.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208445" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-06.50.02.png" alt="" width="680" height="550" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-06.50.54.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208446" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-06.50.54-385x580.png" alt="" width="385" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-06.50.54-385x580.png 385w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-06.50.54-598x900.png 598w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-06.50.54-768x1156.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-06.50.54.png 788w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 385px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-06.52.17.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208447" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-06.52.17-385x580.png" alt="" width="385" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-06.52.17-385x580.png 385w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-06.52.17-598x900.png 598w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-06.52.17-768x1156.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-04-06.52.17.png 788w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 385px" /></a></p><p>專門報道 Rockstar 新聞的外媒 <a href="http://GTABase.com">GTABase.com</a> 指出，影片由 Rockstar Games 其中一位開發者的兒子洩露，但未有列出證據，亦未能證實影片的內容是否屬實，對預告片發布前流出洩密片感到失望。不過 <a href="http://GTABase.com">GTABase.com</a> 又稱，洩密片段或有可能由冒充 Rockstar Games 開發者的第三方發布。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">BREAKING:</p><p>In a totally unexpected turn of events, it appears the ‘leaked’ footage has come from the son of a Rockstar Games employee. <a href="https://t.co/T8oyT42hSE">pic.twitter.com/T8oyT42hSE</a></p><p>&mdash; GTABase.com (@GTABase) <a href="https://twitter.com/GTABase/status/1731009471994818872?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">December 2, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>圖片來源：影片截圖</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/gta-6-tiktok-leak-has-come-from-the-son-of-a-rockstar-games-employee">Eurogamer</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>====</p><h2>unwire learn 推出:</h2><p><strong>獨門 AI 用法助你工作及創業課程</strong><br /><a href="https://learn.unwire.hk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">&lt;按此報名&gt;</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/04/gta-6/game-channel/">GTA 6 影片遭洩密，開發者親兒子抖音流出影片</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
